  schema:name "How to Trace the State-Aesthetic Continuum of an Image" ;
  schema:description "A procedure for taking a single image, clip, or short artifact and locating it across the state-aesthetic continuum: which positions it occupies, which conventions it has migrated, and which institutional cover it is presented under versus which it formally inhabits." ;
